    <prp:abstract>We propose a deep map with ALMA at subarcsecond resolution in band 7 to reveal the location and morphology of the inner belt around Fomalhaut, a benchmark for debris systems. The proposed observations will allow us to confirm a tentative detection of the belt from our cycle-1 data and provide new insights into Fomalhaut's terrestrial zone. </prp:abstract>
